quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  11,89,"Eehmon yim…ďe am, wata nga√Īngu am defu on haa he…ďa on sifa ko he…ďnoo yim…ďe Nuuhu maa yim…ďe Huudi maa yim…ďe Saalih. Yim…ďe Luuti …ďen kan ngo…ó…óaani on."
  11,90,"Imsinanee Joomi mon, refti tuubanon mo. Pelet Joomi am ko jurmotoo…óo, Gi…óo"."
  11,91,"∆Āe mbi'i: "eeheyma Shu'aybu, men alah faamude ko …óuu…ói e …óuum ko mbi'ataa; minen mi…óen ma nji'a hakku-nde amen lo'o…óo. Si wanaano gorol maa ngol, men piyirteno kee∆īe. Aan a wonaani teddu…óo e amen"."
  11,92,"O maaki: "E ko gorol am ngol …ďuri teddudo e mon diini Alla, on wa…ótirii mo …ďaawo mon hawkaa…óo? Pellet Joomi am ko hu…ďindii…óo(fiiltiido) ko ngollaton kon."
  11,93,"Eeheymon yim…ďe am, ngollee e nokku mo'on. miin kadi ko mi golloowo. Arma nde nganndoton ko hombo lepte koynooje arat e mu'm e ko hommbo woni penoowo on. (Jooni non) padee! min kadi mi…óo won¬īdi e mon patndii…óo."
  11,94,"Nde yamiroore amen nden arnoo, min da…óndiri Shu'aybu e …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe won¬īdu…ďe e makko yurmeende amen. Haacaango ngon nanngi …ďen too√Ī…ďe, …ďe wa…ótini ka cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe jiccii…ďe(.jus…ďe)"
  11,95,"A wi'ay …ďe √Īii…ďaano …óon. ngandee wo…ó…óineede yurmeende wonanii Madayana wano Samuuda'en wo…ó…óiniranoo."
  11,96,"GooŇč…óii Men Nulirii Muusaa Aayeeje amen …óeen e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  11,97,"Ha e Fir'awna e mbatu mun. …ďe njokkii yamiroore Fir'awna nden, yamiroore Fir'awna non wanaa feewnde."